                    This app is Task Management system that has the ability to take 
                    users schedule, 
                    record on a table and sort them using date and time by priotising 
                    the ones the will immediately happans. 
                    The App allows users to create, update, and delete task. 
                    Users can also organize tasks by proirty and set deadlines.
                    The system is scalable, secure and optimized for performance.
                </p>
