            <div class="disc">
                <h2>Core Functionalities</h2>
                <p>The system has the following Functionalities:</p>
                <dl>
                    <dt>Users Resgistration and Authenticatiuon:</dt>
                    <dd>- A secure registration and login system using
                        JSON or sesions.</dd>
                    <dd>- Include Password hashing using bcrypt.</dd>

                    <dt>Task Management:</dt>
                    <dd>- Users can create task with attributes such as title,
                        description, deadline and priority</dd>
                    <dd>- Users can update or delete tasks.</dd>

                    <dt>Task Filtering:</dt>
                    <dd>- The app include filtering system where users can filter tasks
                        based on priority or due date</dd>
                    
                    <dt>Search Functionality:</dt>
                    <dd>- Users can search for task based on keywords in the 
                        title or description.</dd>
                    
                </dl>
